{"article_id":"A6ZLB5tEDplEgmV6","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Muslim husband and wife behind the mass shooting in San Bernardino began erasing their digital footprint a day in advance of the deadly attack ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"deleting email accounts ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"disposing of hard drives","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"and smashing their cellphones ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"according to law enforcement investigators","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"who are treating the probe as a counterterrorism case .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Investigators edged closer Thursday to the conclusion","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that Syed Rizwan Farook and his wife , Tashfeen Malik , were radicalized by Islamist extremists either in the U.S. or during trips to the Middle East ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"including Saudi Arabia .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Working to determine","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"whether terrorism was the motive in the attack at a government-organized holiday party ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"officials scrambled to re-create the travels , contacts and lifestyle of Farook , a 28-year-old U.S. citizen of Pakistani descent , and his 27-year-old Pakistani wife .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Intelligence sources said","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"there is still no explicit evidence","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"linking the two to known terrorists on U.S. or foreign watch lists","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"and that the couple was not on the FBI ' s radar before Wednesday ' s deadly shooting rampage .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"But their cache of thousands of rounds of ammunition and explosives","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"found in a home","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"that the couple rented","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"raises major concerns about a wider plot , or a plan","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"to act on their own","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"to hit other targets .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Authorities have tracked down at least four people from the Los Angeles area","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"who were previously under investigation by U.S. counterterrorism officials","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"and were found to have had communication with Farook in the past ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"said a law enforcement source","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"involved in the investigation .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"But details about the individuals were murky .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"The law enforcement source said","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"the last contact","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"any of the four had with Farook","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"was in June ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"and asserted","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"that nothing fruitful came from the interviews about Wednesday ' s attack .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Rand Paul :","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Those","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"who dissed prayer after California attack","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"are ' snide , snotty , and arrogant '","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"With that as a backdrop , officials were working Thursday night","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"to determine what motivated Farook and Malik to storm a conference room inside the Inland Regional Center during a holiday party","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"and spray the room with bullets .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Fourteen people were killed","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"and another 21 were injured in either the shooting or a police pursuit and gunbattle","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"that occurred hours later .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"The San Bernardino County sheriff-coroner ' s office continued to work at the scene of the massacre","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"documenting evidence","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"and removing several of the bodies","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"that remained .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"It was not until Thursday afternoon that officials had contacted the next of kin for all 14 of the victims","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"and that their names were publicly released .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Farook and Malik died in the firefight","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"as they tried to evade police in a rented SUV ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"firing 76 rounds at officers","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"who unleashed 380 rounds of their own","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"and riddled the vehicle with bullet holes .","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"More than 1,500 rounds of unspent ammunition were found in the vehicle ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"according to police .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"One official ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"who spoke anonymously with The ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"cautioned against jumping to conclusions .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"The official said","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"the investigation is still young","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"and asserted","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"that \" radicalization can happen in a number of different inflection points and in a number of different ways .","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"It ' s not a one-size-fits-all sort of thing . \"","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"But fresh details continued to emerge about the background of the two -","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"supporting the notion","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"that the attack was planned","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"and not a spur-of-the-moment response to a party snub or quarrel .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"The couple had a 6-month-old daughter ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"who was left in a relative ' s care","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"before they stormed the Inland Regional Center","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"bedecked in tactical-style clothes","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"and spraying 75 rounds into the conference room .","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"Three pipe bombs","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"configured as one large explosive device","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"were recovered from the center .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Police also found bomb-making materials , 12 pipe bombs and more than 4,500 rounds of ammunition inside the couple ' s home .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"\" This is not your average investigation , \"","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"said David Bowdich , assistant director in charge of the FBI ' s Los Angeles field office ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"mentioning the multiple crime scenes , victims and recovered evidence .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"\" It will take time . \"","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Officials","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"involved in the investigation","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"the couple appeared to have gone to great lengths","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"to conceal themselves","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"and make difficult investigation of their plans","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"- further suggesting premeditation .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"A cellphone","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"recovered from Malik ' s body","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"was newly purchased","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"and had been used only recently .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Two other cellphones","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"that were recovered","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"had been smashed with a hammer","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"and were expected to be sent to the FBI ' s forensic lab in Washington for examination .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Authorities also noted","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"that a hard drive and motherboard were missing from a computer","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"found at the Redlands , California , home","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"that the couple rented .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"Farook worked as a health inspector for the San Bernardino County Health Department , the agency","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"holding the holiday party .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"He had been in attendance at the event","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"but was reported to have left","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"and returned about 30 minutes later with his wife .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Accounts have emerged","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"that Farook was engaged in a dispute with someone at the party","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"before he left ,","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"but police at a Thursday press conference said","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"they were still investigating the information","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"and had varying stories from witnesses .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"\" There appears to be a degree of planning","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that went into this , \"","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"said San Bernardino Police Chief Jarrod Burguan .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"\" Nobody just gets upset at a party","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"and goes home","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"and plans an attack like that . \"","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"The State Department confirmed Thursday","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"that Malik held a Pakistani passport","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"and was in the U.S. on a K-1 visa","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"reserved for fiancees of U.S. citizens .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"Department spokesman Mark Toner told reporters","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"that Malik was granted the visa in Islamabad","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"and would have had to undergo \" counterterrorism screening \"","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"to receive the document from U.S. authorities .","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"While other officials said","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"the visa was issued in 2014 ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"details about international travel by Farook ' s and Malik ' s travels were not fully clear .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"Investigators said","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"Farook traveled at one point to Pakistan","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"before returning to the U.S. in July 2014 with his bride-to-be .","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"Sources also confirmed","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"that Farook went to Saudi Arabia for nine days in summer 2014 .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"It was unclear whether the couple traveled to other countries together .","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"Mr. Toner told reporters","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"that the State Department does not track the movements of U.S. citizens overseas .","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"The official","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"who spoke anonymously with The Times","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"it was entirely possible that the couple had contact with extremists during their foreign travels or while in the U.S. ,","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"but that the extent of those contacts was unclear .","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"\" If you ' re in a minority in whatever country","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"you ' re in ,","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"a lot of the relationships may be tight-knit ,","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"so the chance","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"that you ' re going to have contacts with people","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"that may be of interest to authorities ,","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"that ' s plausible , \"","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"the official said .","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"\" But the chance","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"that there ' s a close relationship there","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"is unknown","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"and won ' t be known until further investigation . \"","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"Farook ' s brother-in-law , Farhan Khan , said Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"that he was shocked by Farook ' s actions .","depth":7},{"id":157,"text":"\" I have no idea , no idea ,","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"why he would do that .","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"Why he would do something like this , \"","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"Mr. Khan said .","depth":7},{"id":161,"text":"Two weeks ago , Farook and one of the co-workers","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"he killed ,","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"52-year-old Nicholas Thalasinos , had a heated conversation about Islam ,","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"according to Kuuleme Stephens , a friend of the victim ' s .","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"Ms. Stephens said","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"she happened to call Mr. Thalasinos","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"while he was at work","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"and having a discussion with Farook .","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":170,"text":"Mr. Thalasinos told her","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"that Farook \" doesn ' t agree","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"that Islam is not a peaceful religion . \"","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"Other co-workers recalled bits and pieces about the man ,","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"whom many viewed as mild-mannered and happy .","depth":7},{"id":175,"text":"Co-worker Patrick Baccari said","depth":7},{"id":176,"text":"he was sitting at the same table as Farook during the holiday party","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"when he suddenly disappeared .","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"Mr. Baccari said","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"when the shooting started ,","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"he took refuge in a bathroom","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"and suffered minor wounds from shrapnel slicing through the wall .","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"The shooting lasted about five minutes ,","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"when he looked in the mirror","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"he realized","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"he was bleeding .","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"\" If I hadn ' t been in the bathroom ,","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"I ' d probably be laying dead on the floor , \"","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"Mr. Baccari described Farook as reserved","depth":8},{"id":193,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"he showed no signs of unusual behavior .","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"Earlier this year , he traveled to Saudi Arabia ,","depth":9},{"id":196,"text":"was gone for about a month","depth":11},{"id":197,"text":"and returned with a wife ,","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"and later grew a beard ,","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"Mr. Baccari said .","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"⦁ This article is based in part on wire reports .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":401,"left":400,"right":200,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":400,"left":319,"right":399,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":319,"left":234,"right":318,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":206,"right":233,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":204,"right":205,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":0,"right":203,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":203,"left":1,"right":202,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":202,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":205,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":221,"right":232,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":221,"left":208,"right":220,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":6,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":210,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":209,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":209,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":219,"left":213,"right":218,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":213,"left":12,"right":212,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":212,"left":211,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":211,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"p